      <title>FDIC下令面对SVB财务诉讼，寻求19亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/fdic-ordered-to-face-svb-financial-suit-seeking-1-9-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州的一名联邦法官裁定，联邦存款保险公司必须面对一项诉讼，要求偿还1930亿美元的政府机构在2023年硅谷银行倒闭后扣押。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/fdic-ordered-to-face-svb-financial-suit-seeking-1-9-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 00:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
